<h3>News</h3>
<div class="story">

<h4>Lin&#160;retires</h4>
	<p>Lin Skelton is well known to many of our customers as their first point of contact with <span class="caps">MMS</span>. But now, having put off retirement several times, she has finally decided that holidaying is better than working! </p>

	<p>In the 12 years she has worked here she has taken on so many roles:- scheduler, training coordinator, order processor, PA, office manager etc. In fact there were very few tasks that Lin didn&#8217;t take on and all completed with a smile and her customary professionalism. </p>

	<p>We shall miss you Lin but wish you the best for the future.</p>

